The rpiaddon is a Raspberry Pi Add On board by Damian Melson. See
https://github.com/damianmelson/Add-On-Board
and
http://forum.fhem.de/index.php/topic,14156.msg89058.html#msg89058
for details.

FLASHING FIRMWARE

To update firmware with culfw execute:

	make program

on the raspberry pi. This will require some tools installed upfront. 
Use:

	apt-get install make avrdude


to flash the recompiled rpiaddon.hex file. It has support for InfraRed Rx  
compiled in.

USING

The culfw stack is available on: /dev/ttyAMA0@38400
